automation-platform/
├── docker-compose.yml
├── kubernetes/
├── packages/
│   ├── api-service/
│   ├── crawler-service/
│   ├── execution-service/
│   ├── ai-service/
│   ├── scheduler-service/
│   └── shared/
├── infrastructure/
└── README.md

Key components:

API Service (Express/Fastify) - receives user requests, enqueues jobs
Queue System (BullMQ + Redis)
Crawler Service (Crawlee + Playwright)
Execution Service (Playwright + Browser Pool)
AI Service (Claude/GPT-4 integration)
Scheduler Service (cron jobs for remapping)
Session Manager
Selector Engine (multi-fallback)
Proxy Manager
Storage (Postgres + Redis)
Observability (Prometheus metrics)
Docker + K8s configs
